# Google Drive Progress Report Updates

The owner maintains the CRM & Website progress report on Google Drive. The agent has no access to it.

## When to provide updates

After completing work sessions, or when the user asks (e.g. "اعطني التحديث للـ Drive", "give me the Drive update"), provide **plain English text** ready to copy and paste — not a .doc/.docx file.

## Format

Use this structure each time:

```
Update — [Month Day, Year]

Completed in this session:
- ...
- ...

Still remaining:
- ...

Verification:
- ...
```

## Rules

- Default language: **English** (unless the user asks for Arabic).
- Append-style: each update is a new dated section for the bottom of the Drive document.
- When an item moves from "Remaining" to "Done", state that explicitly.
- Base updates on actual git changes, code work, and requirements-audit.md when relevant.
- Do not generate Word files for owner follow-up unless explicitly requested.

